title: Katy Brand New Community 4 Weeks FREE
posting_body: ['For leasing information call or text', 'show contact info', 'today!!!', 'Ask for ID# 2884A', 'Choose your perfect floor plan from our studio, one, two, and three bedroom options featuring walk-in closets, oversized soaking tubs, designer wood-style flooring, and spacious patios.', 'Each home is carefully crafted with an open-concept gourmet kitchen, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and custom kitchen cabinetry.', 'With convenient access to Grand Parkway and the University of Houston Katy campus, we are the perfect combination of suburban ease and urban flair.', 'If you are looking for an exceptional apartment home in West Houston, look no further.', 'We look forward to welcoming you home!', 'Chef inspired kitchen with under-mount sink and subway tile backsplash', 'Island with wine rack and conversational seating (select plans)', 'Ambient under counter lighting', 'Stainless steel appliance package', '42" upper cabinetry with brushed nickel accents', 'Granite countertops throughout', 'Luxurious bathrooms with custom framed mirrors', 'Oversized soaking tubs/walk-in showers (select plans)', 'Spacious closets', "Open plans with 9'-12' ceilings (varies by floor level/plan)", 'Patio or balcony (select plans)', 'Modern lighting with contemporary accents', 'Designer tile and wood style flooring throughout', 'HE, front load washer and dryer', 'Intrusion alarms']
